            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Hero Section -->


    <!-- Start Product Section -->
    <div class="product-section" style="background-color: #EFF2F1">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">

          <!-- Start Column 1 -->
          <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-3 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
            <h2 class="mb-4 section-title">Crafted with Precision.</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">Built with premium materials to deliver performance and durability.Designed for efficiency,
              innovation, and style—ready to power your next big idea. </p>
            <p><a href="shop.html" class="btn">Explore</a></p>
          </div>
          <!-- End Column 1 -->

          <!-- Start Column 2 -->
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4 col-lg-3 mb-5 mb-md-0">
            <a class="product-item" href="cart.html">
              <img src="images/lapbig.png" class="img-fluid product-thumbnail">
              <h3 class="product-title">Gaming Laptop</h3>
              <strong class="product-price">₹82000</strong>

              <span class="icon-cross">
                <img src="images/cross.svg" class="img-fluid">
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <!-- End Column 2 -->

          <!-- Start Column 3 -->
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4 col-lg-3 mb-5 mb-md-0">
            <a class="product-item" href="cart.html">
              <img src="images/gaming.png" class="img-fluid product-thumbnail">
              <h3 class="product-title">Business Laptop</h3>
              <strong class="product-price">₹68000</strong>

              <span class="icon-cross">
                <img src="images/cross.svg" class="img-fluid">
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <!-- End Column 3 -->

          <!-- Start Column 4 -->
          <div class="col-12 col-md-4 col-lg-3 mb-5 mb-md-0">
            <a class="product-item" href="cart.html">
              <img src="images/student.png" class="img-fluid product-thumbnail">
              <h3 class="product-title">Student Laptop</h3>
              <strong class="product-price">₹55000</strong>

              <span class="icon-cross">
                <img src="images/cross.svg" class="img-fluid">
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <!-- End Column 4 -->

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Product Section -->

    <!-- Start Why Choose Us Section -->
    <div class="why-choose-section" style="background-color: #EFF2F1">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-between">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
            <p>Experience high-performance laptops designed for every need, from work to play. Our commitment to quality
              ensures you get the best technology to support your ambitions.</p>

            <div class="row my-5">
              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img src="images/truck.svg" alt="Image" class="imf-fluid">
                  </div>
                  <h3><b>Fast &amp;Free Shipping</b> </h3>
                  <p>Get your laptop delivered quickly and without any extra cost, straight to your doorstep.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img src="images/bag.svg" alt="Image" class="imf-fluid">
                  </div>
                  <h3><b>Easy to Shop</b></h3>
                  <p>Our website is designed for easy browsing and purchasing, helping you find the perfect laptop with
                    just a few clicks.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img src="images/support.svg" alt="Image" class="imf-fluid">
                  </div>
                  <h3><b>24/7 Support</b></h3>
                  <p>We’re here for you anytime, with round-the-clock customer service to assist you with all your
                    laptop-related needs.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <img src="images/return.svg" alt="Image" class="imf-fluid">
                  </div>
                  <h3><b>Hassle Free Returns</b></h3>
                  <p>Not satisfied with your purchase? Enjoy easy returns and exchanges with our no-hassle return
                    policy.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-5">
            <div class="img-wrap">
              <img src="images/White gaming Laptop 2023.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Why Choose Us Section -->

    <!-- Start We Help Section -->
    <div class="we-help-section" style="background-color:#EFF2F1">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-between">
          <div class="col-lg-7 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
            <div class="imgs-grid">
              <div class="grid grid-1"><img src="images/Mac Book Pro IPRIME.jpg" alt="Untree.co"></div>
              <div class="grid grid-2"><img src="images/mSi.jpg" alt="Untree.co"></div>
              <div class="grid grid-3"><img src="images/vilote (1).jpg" alt="Untree.co"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 ps-lg-5">
            <h2 class="section-title mb-4"><b>We Help You Make Modern Interior Design</b></h2>
            <p>Donec facilisis quam ut purus rutrum lobortis. Donec vitae odio quis nisl dapibus malesuada. Nullam ac
